DESCRIPTION:Organizer: OCPL - Aliso Viejo Branch\\nCost: free\\nAges: 0-60
  months\\nCategory: Music & Dance\\n\\nJoin us for a music appreciation se
 ries. Music lovers of all ages are invited to visit the library and enjoy 
 a performance by one of the world's premier guzheng (Chinese zither) music
 ians\, Bei Bei.\n\nNo registration required\, all ages welcome.\n\nThis pr
 oject is funded in part through a grant from the California Department of 
 Aging and administered locally by the Orange County Office on Aging.\\n\\n
 More info: https://ocpl.libcal.com/event/16590700
LOCATION:Aliso Viejo\, Aliso Viejo
